# Arabic Language & RTL Support Guidelines

## 🌍 Language Priority
Arabic is the **primary language** for this Saudi Arabia-focused platform. English is secondary.

## 🔤 Typography Rules
- **Primary Font**: `font-tajawal` (Tajawal font family)
- **Fallbacks**: Noto Sans Arabic, system-ui, sans-serif
- **Font configuration**: [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) line 22-23

## 📝 Content Guidelines
### Arabic Text Best Practices
- Use proper Arabic typography and spacing
- Ensure correct Arabic punctuation (،؛؟)
- Use Arabic-Indic numerals when appropriate (٠١٢٣٤٥٦٧٨٩)
- Maintain cultural context and terminology

### Translation Keys Structure
